attributes.name: Dino Sunglasses
attributes.description: Sunglasses in a pilot look in shades of blue, brown and black with differently coloured lenses. A striking model for men.

customFields.articleDesc: Sunglasses in a pilot look in shades of blue, brown and black with differently coloured lenses. A striking model for men.
customFields.articleText: Each model of the new Dino sunglasses series comes in different shades of colour. The shape resembles the look of pilot's glasses in a new angular format and shows in its owning toning a noble character with an extra pinch of collness. Small nose plates allow a variable carrying capacity, as the fine plates individuallay adjust themselfes to every nose while wearing the sunglasses. In a fashionable, discreet lettering, the brand name AIGNER is presented on the outside of the filigree temples. These glasses are a must-have and an acquisition for eternity, because the style remains timeless and always trendy.
